project.name: Russian Rust Language Community
project.description: Our community for russian speaking peoples, who working or interesting in Rust programming language. Our goal is to popularize Rust language in post-USSR countries. We translate articles and announcements, organize meetups, and support forums for Russian rust-related talks.
project.license_type: For translations - inherits from original books/articles, other part of our activities is meetups and we are open to all people interested in Rust.
